Type: Package
Package: truncpois
Title: Truncated Poisson Distribution
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-04-05
Authors@R: c(
    person("Arun", "Sundar Paulraj", , "arun.paulraj.2026@mumail.ie", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Keefe", "Murphy", , "keefe.murphy@mu.ie", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Provides functions for the truncated Poisson distribution,
    including density (dtruncpois), cumulative distribution function
    (ptruncpois), quantile function (qtruncpois), and random generation
    (rtruncpois).  Also includes functions for the mean (extruncpois),
    variance (vartruncpois), median (mtruncpois), and mode
    (mode_truncpois) of the truncated Poisson distribution.
